List of specifications for this program

Big Dream:
- login page (username, password, password recovery)
- home page with buttons leading to previous categroies users have made, friends' categories, and way to start new category
- way to unpload .jpg and .gif files
- way to store files that have been uploaded within their users' categories
- button to click through files
- way to follow/connect friends
- way to share to Facebook

First Steps:
- start with create new page
- add image page
- swipe through images
